    "Task and document forms choose visible sections by workflow configuration.",
    "<Form Blocks> | Subject is special and must be first in task forms.",
    "Documents and Temporary Documents are separate section/content paths even when both reuse <DocumentListItem>.",
    "Prefer prepared attachment variants when the requested scenario matches one of them."
